{"tid":1620861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（香港進化史）快閃行動已成主流","createTime":"2019-10-04T11:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T11:52:20.000Z","uid":99654,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"21a66beb29d26309cfc1ede1755ea2e559ca59d4","tid":1620861,"uid":99654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"依幾日開始有唔同區嘅快閃行動出現 好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先好多謝大家有份出席同埋參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係依到大力咁支持同埋推快閃行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家留意下 依幾日被捕人數相對以往遊行示威後嘅活動安全得多 而且參與人數都係可以接受嘅範圍內 重點係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">做到嘅野比起以往仲多</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日柒婆條仆街要用緊急法推蒙面法 正正就中左我地嘅目標 既然我地正面打唔贏Full Gear嘅狗仔 咁不如大家用快閃行動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原因一</span></span>：可以確保手足係冇狗嘅情況下做野 減低被即場拘捕嘅機會 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原因二</span></span>：快閃現場冇防唔等於狗仔唔洗做 佢地只不過係遲左到 但對快閃行動嘅手足黎做已經足夠 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為你地黎到只可以食空氣 手足走曬啦</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家繼續快閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係撚時撚記得睇情況咁撚 人少冇支援要低調小心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"80a6a8f44b9a4617499071a37eafb5e2f4bb976e","tid":1620861,"uid":99654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:39:31.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gi